Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門灣悲劇隨光芒溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灼焦視網膜的屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木驅使著GUNDAM1號機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與2號機展開最後之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為將宿命打上休止符而被牽引在一起的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決鬥無止盡地持續著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但浦木並不知道那只是「星塵」的序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩架GUNDAM消失於所羅門之海時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「星塵」終於顯露出其真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}「玫瑰人生」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉茲閣下的艦隊由左舷接近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將會合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達各艦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行對希瑪艦隊的補給作業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我眼前浮現著賈布羅慌亂的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，會回以什麼答覆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然，不管如何答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星塵作戰的目標是不會變更的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箭已射出了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉茲怎麼會接受這種要求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且即使在月球扔下了殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也絲毫動搖不了聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且不管其真正用意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果對目前政局造成不良影響…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想維持政權嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就月球的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都有一致的認識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才叫平民統治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，對新的阻礙者…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克西斯來的艦隊該如何處置？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持中立的話允許他們有期限地停留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要特地與之為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在向月球移動的殖民地在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這是金米島的殘存艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大戰速的艦隊能在殖民地墜落前捕捉到敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並將其擊潰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將殖民地移動用推進燃料點燃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的意圖就挫敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃蕩海盜也就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在劫持殖民地時為何不使用推進燃料呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還特地用殖民地相撞…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為沒有足以點燃的能量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙還是安靜點好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0068,,{\fs38}阿克西斯先遣艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你們的作戰感佩之至
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也非常渴望能盡量加以協助啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了這中立的阿克西斯艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才能無後顧之憂地戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事成之後士兵的回收請務必…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我可以發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是阿克西斯一點小小的餞行禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿是ZION精神的實體化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是MA「Neue Ziel」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}Neue Ziel：型號AMX-002 阿克西斯製造的宇宙戰用試作型重MA\N機體上裝有I FIELD發生器，使敵方光束武器攻擊無效化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目測「玫瑰人生」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離8000
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光傳感器開放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是「玫瑰人生」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始導航
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脈衝照射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接前10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導航光正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對速度11
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要接收3號機了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？悶悶不樂的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上陸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜仍然反對我駕駛3號機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行系留作業
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是阿納海姆最大的艦隻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合做3號機的測試基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備接駁舷梯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說宏，3號機是怎樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實體只有妮娜和艦長知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是什麼宇宙空間據點防衛用的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據點防衛用？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好駕駛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼機體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉前來報到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM的駕駛員就是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是401警戒中隊的納卡哈·中門少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你是GUNDAM的機師也告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾比昂在入港期間將納入本中隊的管理之下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除阿爾比昂追擊迪拉茲艦隊的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新任務是擔任「玫瑰人生」及GUNDAM3號機的警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請、請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點接收3號機並阻止墜落的殖民地的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地交給金米島的追擊艦隊就行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們得到了高雲將軍非正式允諾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM開發計劃已不再由高雲將軍管轄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變成這樣的理由你們也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2號機被奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閱艦式被搞得亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉為遞交戰鬥數據
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能與我同行「玫瑰人生」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上陸的只限艦長和妮娜·巴普爾頓還有他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦還真一本正經地答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要得到阿克西斯先遣艦隊認可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就達到目的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希瑪在行動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正照預定行事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來「玫瑰人生」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是所長克蕾娜·哈克謝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿爾比昂艦長席那普斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是浦木中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了，所長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望能讓其他人一起上陸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已見過中門少佐了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是負責GUNDAM3號機開發的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是露雪特·奧德比
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你精神很好呢，露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說1號機的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真嚴重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉，我聽說過你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你也精通MS理論
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必擔任3號機的試飛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃已暫時中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不能讓他駕駛3號機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號機已經完成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下修正實用方面的數據而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須執行命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上就是中止開發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是，軍方到底在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中門少佐一到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把測試人員遣回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開發1號機的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能瞭解我的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有測試機師的話研究也無法繼續…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是完美的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成的話一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把浦木中尉讓給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的瞬間的機動判斷力、未來預測
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是能在理解機械的情況下操作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的話就算是3號機複雜的武器管理系統…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用得著那麼生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已趕不上戰局了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是失去了1號機而失常了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了，是殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與本隊聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先鋒軍已捕捉到敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥配置，進入炮擊戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上方11時角度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高熱源體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭上？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉沒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，中門少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱、抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打擾一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我有東西要給中尉看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我？難道是3號機？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是3號機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾的是數據大多被中門少佐接管了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在手上只有這些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:15:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信，這全部是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？能駕駛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否要取得3號機就看你的決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是違反命令的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不正是需要3號機之時嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這是為的什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的人也會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了保衛聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的好答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉已經接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你一定要這麼拚命呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在這裏磨蹭的話卡多他們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要換衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經上了月球的繞行軌道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的救命稻草的聯邦軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在卡多面前束手束腳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始調整鏡面角度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1號啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開起爆聚光器的回路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想把殖民地扔到月球上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:17:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才教你解救馮·布朗的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，只剩下兩條路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被殖民地壓得上西天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地獲得推力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始加速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將殖民地移動用的推進燃料點燃？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會、會往哪去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到推力的殖民地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫離月球繞行軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後，這回會被地球引力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地墜落的真正目標是地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會是一年戰爭悲劇的重演
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離地球還有38小時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼要佯攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，是要讓追擊艦隊耗盡推進燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間猶豫了，浦木中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是瑪德拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們推進燃料用盡，無法續航
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是蒙哥列
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推力下降，脫離陣形
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生，這樣下去還能剩幾艘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補給艦何時才能到達？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉，這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐，阿爾比昂的機師到工場區去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:18:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他揪出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他碰到3號機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是抵抗的話，准許開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時可以開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機正好啊，中尉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…並不是Core Block System
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}Core Block System：核心操作艙系統
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…那個尾翼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也兼做連接系統的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格了，中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，詳情稍後再談
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了，浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是在做什麼？中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，離開GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是在嚇唬人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉，快進駕駛艙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這邊來，現在還可以不問罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你對現狀的判斷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把平民當做盾牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪取3號機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.29,0:21:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且殺害平民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就該受軍法會議處分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我代為行刑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子塞住的混蛋們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點扔掉槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐，嫁禍於人太不識趣了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙幾時…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請撤掉士兵，中門少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的敵人應該是迪拉茲艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.55,0:21:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，你來照料
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生，快叫醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請照顧好3號機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一開始就已知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你反對3號機的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指我和宏的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，你並不只是在擔心他的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最害怕的事是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生，快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在3年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月球…3年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:22:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和卡多大尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往過的事我都知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.93,0:23:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不願再見到他們兩人的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.05,0:23:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號機…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將3號機…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露雪特
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請祝福露雪特·奧德比
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.20,0:24:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這能叫做MS嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.06,0:24:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.01,0:24:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切換自動的時機…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.71,0:24:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看賦值監視器
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.89,0:24:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝甲內櫃的武器載入要在3秒以內
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.96,0:25:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟隨而來的敵人也到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.05,0:25:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有新敵機
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.80,0:25:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但數據裏並沒有這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.11,0:27:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預    告
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.94,0:27:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止界限點
